---
source: crates/audiomirror-cli/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: output
---
Capture from a local mic and play back on a local output device (loopback test).

Example: audiomirror-cli loop --input <mic-id> --output <spk-id>

Usage: audiomirror-cli loop [OPTIONS] --input <INPUT> --output <OUTPUT>

Options:
      --input <INPUT>
          

      --output <OUTPUT>
          

      --bitrate <BITRATE>
          [default: 64000]

      --source <SOURCE>
          [default: mic]
          [possible values: mic, system]

      --fec-mode <FEC_MODE>
          [default: auto]
          [possible values: auto, always, never]

      --simulated-loss-pct <SIMULATED_LOSS_PCT>
          [default: 0]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
